• UAE (20 percent)—almost all in its Knowledge Village
• Qatar (nine percent)
• Singapore (seven percent)
• Canada (six percent)
• Malaysia  (six  percent)—[good  overview  on  situation  in  Malaysia  in  OBHE
• China (five percent)
